---
import Base from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';import {site,mailto} from '../config/site';
const schema={'@context':'https://schema.org','@type':'ContactPage',name:'Contact INNO',description:'Email INNO about transformer temperature products.',url:new URL('/contact/',site.siteUrl).toString()};
---
<Base title="Contact INNO for Transformer Temperature Products" description="Email INNO about transformer OTI, WTI, BWY, BWR and oil temperature monitoring device selection, datasheets, drawings and quotations." schema={schema}><section class="page-hero"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Direct email contact</p><h1>Send Your Transformer Temperature Requirement</h1><p>No form is used on this website. Email the model and engineering requirement directly to INNO.</p><div class="actions"><a class="button" href={mailto('Transformer temperature product inquiry')}>Email {site.email}</a></div></div></section><section class="section"><div class="container grid two"><article class="prose"><h2>Include these selection details</h2><ul class="email-checklist"><li>Transformer type and rating</li><li>OTI, WTI or monitoring requirement</li><li>Existing model and nameplate photo</li><li>Measuring range</li><li>Switch quantity and purpose</li><li>Pt100, 4-20 mA or RS485 output</li><li>Power supply</li><li>Capillary length</li><li>Bulb size and mounting thread</li><li>Mounting drawing</li><li>Quantity and destination country</li><li>Requested delivery date</li></ul></article><article class="card"><h2>Email address</h2><p><a class="text-link" href={`mailto:${site.email}`}>{site.email}</a></p><p>Attach drawings and photographs directly to your email. Ask for the current datasheet, outline drawing, terminal diagram and quotation for the selected configuration.</p><a class="button" href={mailto('INNO transformer temperature datasheet and quotation')}>Open email application</a></article></div></section></Base>
